## Folder structure
```
src/
  app/           # Next.js App Router (layout, page, globals.css)
  components/
    navigation/  # DynamicIsland
    hero/        # Hero, FloatingIcons, MatrixCanvas
    projects/    # ProjectsSection, ProjectCard, ProjectModal
    contact/     # ContactFAB
    ui/          # CustomCursor, shared primitives
  providers/     # Providers.tsx, SmoothScrollProvider.tsx
  hooks/         # useMousePosition, useMagneticEffect (future)
  data/          # projects.ts
  types/         # index.ts
  lib/           # gsap setup (future)
```

## Constraints & preferences
- Dark mode ONLY — no light mode toggle
- Custom cursor always active — `cursor: none` on body
- No third-party UI component libraries (MUI, shadcn, etc.)
- Animations must be hardware-accelerated (transform/opacity only)
- All glassmorphic elements use the `.glass`, `.glass-pill`, `.glass-card` CSS classes
- Framer Motion `layout` / `layoutId` for shared element transitions (Project modal expand)
- Don't add error handling or validation for internal/impossible cases
- Keep components lean — no over-abstraction
